title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1983-10-12

description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Minglewood Blues, Ramble On Rose, My Brother Esau, It Must Have Been The Roses, Cassidy, Cumberland Blues, Looks Like Rain-> Might As Well

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Women Are Smarter, He's Gone-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Black Peter-> Not Fade Away, E: Revolution

reviews.review_text:
Madison Sq. 10/12/1983 
Great show,Angels austrailia were mean

Best Aud source This is my favorite aud source for this one.  Some might like the Cohen Nak 700 pull better.  The u87/nak 441 Eaton source has nice bass, but is a bit flat up top.  That was my old favorite, before the 2 newer versions were uploaded.
